'''Aloisea Inyumba''' (28 Ukuboza 1964 - 6 Ukuboza 2012) yari [[Rwanda|umunyapolitiki wo mu Rwanda]], akaba yari Minisitiri w’uburinganire n’iterambere ry’umuryango ndetse akaba umunyamabanga nshingwabikorwa wa komisiyo y’ubumwe n’ubwiyunge .<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20130311012945/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/obituaries/aloisea-inyumba-politician-who-played-a-key-role-in-the-rebuilding-of-rwanda-8527166.html</ref> 

Mu gihe yigaga ibijyanye n'imibereho n'imibereho myiza muri kaminuza ya Makerere muri [[Ubugande|Uganda]], yinjiye mu [[Ishyaka FPR-Inkotanyi|Rwanda Patriotic Front]] . <ref>https://stringfixer.com/tr/Makerere_University</ref>

Amagambo yo kumushyingura yatanzwe na Perezida [[Paul Kagame]] <ref>https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/tea/rwanda-today/news/kagame-leads-nation-in-eulogising-patriot-and-freedom-fighter-inyumba--1313738</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Aloisea Inyumba yavutse ku ya 28 Ukuboza 1964 muri [[Ubugande|Uganda]], avuka ku babyeyi bavuka mu [[Rwanda]].  Yavutse nyuma y’impinduramatwara yo mu Rwanda yo mu 1959, aho hashyizweho repubulika yiganjemo Abahutu benshi, no gutoteza [[abatutsi]] . [2] Mu gihe ababyeyi be bari bakibera mu [[Rwanda]], kandi mbere yuko avuka, se yiciwe mu bwicanyi bwakorewe abatutsi; nyina yaratorotse hamwe na barumuna be batanu maze umuryango uhungira mu mutekano wa [[Uganda]].<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/60757</ref><ref>https://www.inclusivesecurity.org/2013/04/16/aloisea-inyumba-politician-who-played-a-key-role-in-the-rebuilding-of-rwanda/</ref> <ref name="Melvern" />

Inyumba yabayeho mu bwana bwe muri [[Uganda]], arangiza amashuri ye, hanyuma akomereza muri kaminuza ya Makerere i Kampala, abona impamyabumenyi mu mibereho  myiza y'abaturage.  Mu 1985, yabonanye bwa mbere na [[Paul Kagame]],  undi wari impunzi iva mu [[Rwanda]] icyo gihe yari mu gisirikare cy’inyeshyamba cya [[Yoweri Museveni]] . [4] Nyuma y'umwaka umwe, Museveni yigaruriye igihugu maze azamura Kagame na mugenzi we wo mu [[Rwanda]] [[Fred Rwigema|Fred Rwigyema]] kuba abayobozi mu ngabo z’igihugu. [5] Kagame na Rwigyema bafashe iyo myanya, ariko intego yabo nyamukuru kwari ukugaruka  mu gihugu cyabo, kugira ngo borohereze impunzi nuko inyumba nawwe yemera kubafasha<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201212172587.html</ref>.<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201212100133.html</ref> 

== Umwuga wa politiki ==
Nyuma yo gutsinda kwa FPR muri Nyakanga 1994, Inyumba yashyiizwe muri guverinoma nshya y’inzibacyuho.   yari iyobowe Perezida [[Pasteur Bizimungu]],. [8] Yari yashyizweho ku mwanya wa Minisitiri w'Uburinganire n'Iterambere ry'Umuryango, <ref name="Melvern" /> atangira gahunda ikomeye yo kumvisha uruhare rwabo abagore mu kubaka Rwanda.<ref name=":0">https://www.paulkagame.com/inyumba-was-a-very-good-cadre-unique-selfless-leader/</ref> <ref name="Melvern" />

Mu mwaka wa 2011, yongeye kugirwa inshingano yari yarahoze ari Minisitiri w’uburinganire n’iterambere ry’umuryango, uruhare yagize kugeza apfuye mu 2012.<ref>https://cco.ndu.edu/Media/Images/igphoto/2001470845/</ref> 

== Ubuzima bwa muntu n'urupfu ==
Inyumba yashakanye na Dr Richard Masozera, wahoze ari Umuyobozi mukuru w'ikigo gishinzwe indege za gisivili mu Rwanda (RCAA).  Bombi batangiye gukundana igihe bombi bari abanyeshuri muri kaminuza ya Makerere i Kampala. <ref name="Rwirwahira" /> Babyaranye abana babiri, umukobwa n'umuhungu.<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201212110100.html</ref> 

Inyumba yapfuye ku ya 6 Ukuboza 2012 iwe i Kigali.  Yari arwaye kanseri yo mu muhogo,  kandi yari aherutse gusubira mu rugo nyuma yo kwivuriza mu Budage.  Inyumba yahawe imihango yo gushyingura leta mu [[Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y’u Rwanda|Nteko ishinga amategeko y’u Rwanda]] i Kigali kandi amagambo ye yatanzwe na perezida w’igihugu, [[Paul Kagame]] . <ref name="LastRespects" /> Kagame yamusobanuriye ko ari umuyobozi utitanga "wari umukada mwiza kandi usobanutse neza". <ref name="LastRespects" /> Abandi batanze ibiganiro mu muhango wo gushyingura barimo Minisitiri w’ibikorwa by’inama y’abaminisitiri Protais Musoni na visi guverineri wa [[Banki Nkuru y'u Rwanda|Banki nkuru y’u Rwanda]], [[Monique Nsanzabaganwa]] . <ref name=":0" /><ref name="LastRespects" />
